{"tid":1152597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衝著中國人來的！巴基斯坦五星飯店爆槍戰5死","createTime":"2019-05-13T05:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T05:54:21.000Z","uid":47714,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc24768293bf8c9db935017803e63fb6530aad0e","tid":1152597,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-05-12/245299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2019-05-12%2F245299&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihKdOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=101d5399\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-05-12/245299</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/246/5cd7731f21edb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F246%2F5cd7731f21edb.jpg&h=677c6607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦西南部港市瓜達爾（Gwadar）一家名為「明珠大陸酒店」（Pearl Continental Hotel），於當地時間11日下午4時50分遭到持步槍和手榴彈的叛亂分子攻擊，共造成五人死亡及多人輕重傷，事後巴基斯坦分離主義組織「俾路支解放軍」（Balochistan Liberation Army，BLA）坦承犯案，還嗆聲就是針對中國人及其他外來投資者來的。<br />\n<br />\n這家遭到攻擊的是「明珠大陸酒店」（Pearl Continental Hotel）位於中國「一帶一路」重點投資開發的瓜達爾港，是中國及巴基斯坦政府的高級會議場地，四名全副武裝的恐怖份子闖入後，先是射殺警衛並與維和部隊爆發激烈駁火，飯店緊急撤離至少40名中國公民，軍方隨後也護送在港區內工作的53名中國職員離開。<br />\n<br />\n根據半島電視台報導，「俾路支解放軍」發言人Jihand Baloch坦承，這次襲擊事件是針對待在「明珠大陸酒店」內的中國和其他外國投資者而來，該組織反對中國的投資，還稱「帝國主義」侵略，對當地人民沒有好處。<br />\n<br />\n瓜達爾港濱臨阿拉伯海，具有戰略重要性，是中國耗資600億美元的中巴經濟走廊重心，更是「一帶一路」倡議的旗艦項目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/246/5cd771f19540f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F246%2F5cd771f19540f.jpg&h=c5aca398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆發槍戰的明珠大陸酒店為中巴交流重要地點。   圖/<a href=\"http://wikimedia.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikimedia.org&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihKdOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=ca351815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">wikimedia.org</a>"},{"pid":"b8955a2017231a7d38e924c44308576011fa3040","tid":1152597,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"一帶一路<br />\n帶你直上西天"},{"pid":"82744f75214477b667f5b3c020c33be4bb8c8954","tid":1152597,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"又話係中國最好既盟友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9035fba92ebd37713d110634ebd458bd920ff2","tid":1152597,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"俾路支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63ff6807e786170527c5d3154b6c9b26fefab4b","tid":1152597,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"終於黎啦 屠中共屠中共"}]}